The,Australian,Tourism,Data,Warehouse,ATDW,is,the,national,storage,and,distribution,facility,for,Australian,tourism,products,and,destination,information,Its,contents,are,compiled,in,a,standardized,format,and,made,available,to,tourism,business,owners,operators,wholesalers,retailers,and,distributors,for,use,in,their,websites,booking,systems,and,other,digital,channels,Information,stored,in,the,ATDW,covers,accommodations,attractions,destinations,events,guided,tours,rentals,transportation,etc,This,information,can,be,accessed,using,a,SOAP,based,API,that,employs,calls,issued,in,XML,format